"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Posteroanterior view demonstrating left lower lobe collapse, as seen by elevation of the left hemidiaphragm and increased retrocardiac opacification adjacent to the spine. This is accompanied by plate-like atelectasis of the lingula (Nordenstr&ouml;m's sign).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
